**DrupalConnect is a PHP 5.3+ library to connect your application to Drupal using the [Services 3.0](http://drupal.org/project/services) API.**

DrupalConnect aims to truly let you use Drupal as a pure backend data store for your website. Read more in the [Wiki](https://github.com/epicwhale/DrupalConnect/wiki)

**At the moment, this is purely a work in progress. Please do not start using this in production, but for learning, testing or contributing only. When we're ready with v1, we'll take off this message.**

